caller_intent: The caller wanted to send multiple pictures to Heather Johnson without sending multiple emails and inquired about alternative methods like Dropbox or other apps.
resolution_steps: Agent explained texting as an alternative method, confirming the phone number (336-377-9003).
Agent clarified that texts would require Heather to check them the next day.
Caller agreed to text the pictures with a note to Heather.
knowledge_required: Heather Johnson's contact information (email and phone number)
summary: A caller sought to send multiple pictures to Heather Johnson but wanted to avoid multiple emails. The agent provided her email and texting option, leading the caller to choose texting with a note. The call concluded with the caller agreeing to proceed via text.
